msgid "Security"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend.md:294
msgid ""
"**HTTP headers** — [Helmet]{1} is configured to set comprehensive security "
"headers on all responses, including `Content-Security-Policy`, `X-Content-"
"Type-Options`, `X-Frame-Options`, and `Strict-Transport-Security`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend.md:296
msgid ""
"**CORS** — only origins listed in `CORS_ORIGIN` are permitted. In production "
"this is restricted to `https://linkeddata.open-regels.nl` and `https://"
"cpsv.open-regels.nl`. All other origins receive a CORS rejection."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend.md:298
msgid ""
"**Input validation** — type checking is applied to all request inputs. "
"Variable names, DMN identifiers, and SPARQL endpoint URLs are validated "
"before any service call is made. Request body size is limited to 10 MB."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend.md:300
msgid ""
"**Environment variables** — all sensitive configuration (TriplyDB endpoint "
"URLs, Operaton API URLs, CORS origins, eDOCS credentials) is stored in "
"environment variables and never hardcoded. eDOCS-specific variables: "
"`EDOCS_BASE_URL`, `EDOCS_LIBRARY`, `EDOCS_USER_ID`, `EDOCS_PASSWORD`, "
"`EDOCS_STUB_MODE`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend.md:302
msgid ""
"**Error responses** — the central error handler scrubs stack traces and "
"internal context before returning responses to clients, ensuring no "
"implementation details are exposed."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend.md:306
msgid "Dutch Government API Design Rules compliance"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend.md:308
msgid ""
